history.content: Take either Stat 134 or 140, EE126 is a course that should be taken after 70.

children.subject: Stat 134 is generally really hard (at least when I took it). I heard professors are recommending CS students take 70 first and then 126 due to those classes covering more probability applications to computer science than Stat 134 does

history.content: Hi I want to take either ee 126 or stat 134 next semester. I read that ee 126 goes more in depth than stat 134 but I also read that ee 126 assumes that you have taken cs 70. Would it be wise to take ee 126 concurrently with cs 70 or should I take stat 134 instead?
history.subject: EE 126 Concurrently with CS 70
